description: Primes p such that 73 is not a square mod p.
comments: Also, primes p that are not squares mod 73 (from the quadratic reciprocity law). - _Lekraj Beedassy_, Jul 13 2004
links: Vincenzo Librandi, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
prog: (MAGMA) [p: p in PrimesUpTo(443) | not IsSquare(R! 73) where R:= ResidueClassRing(p)]; // _Vincenzo Librandi_, Sep 10 2012
